{
  "stem": "2316.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the scribe would write a paragraph, or a sentence, or a word-- I don't know-- and their name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It meant a great deal to everyone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my father put me on top of the closet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had like a closet, armoire, they call them now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was sitting on top of the closet, and I was watching the people come in and make their donations, their dollar or $0.50 or $0.10, Russian, you know, Polish money.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I would sit on top of the closet with my brother, or sometimes alone, and watch the people come in and go out and go in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was-- I couldn't figure out what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- then surprisingly, the rabbi-- and I remember him with a beard and big, fur shtreimel and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He explained it to me, how it works.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was so fascinated, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so that was a very, very memorable time in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also remember like my aunt and uncle came from-- no, I think it was just my aunt without her uncle-- without her husband came to visit in 1933.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had the biggest, biggest party in town in her honor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean-- and this is an aunt that left when she was 17 or 16 years old for the United States.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she came to visit just before the-- you know, 1933.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the biggest party in town to honor my aunt from America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, everybody came out of the closet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She was like, today, a big celebrity, maybe like O.J.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Simpson.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody gathered and it was so much fun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just delightful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was sitting there listening and asking her stories about America.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
